      "updated": 1784089270521,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A service that creates a private connection\nbetween Azure datacenters and your\non-premise environment.\n\n--> This doesn't go over public internet.\nMore reliability, \nfaster speeds,\nhigher security,\nconsistent latencies",
      "fontSize": 19.873010253906276,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A service that creates a private connection\nbetween Azure datacenters and your\non-premise environment.\n\n--> This doesn't go over public internet.\nMore reliability, \nfaster speeds,\nhigher security,\nconsistent latencies",
      "autoResize": true,
